What does it take to be a professional sugarcraft artist?
 Cake decorator and sugarcraft sculptor Ann Pickard runs the Icing Centre in Weston-super-Mare, Somerset, and is exhibiting at Cake International at the Birmingham National Exhibition Centre.
 She reveals the secrets of her sculptures and shares how to create a flower decoration. 
 To see the enhanced content on this page, you need to have JavaScript enabled and Adobe Flash installed. 
